e"><span style="width:100%"><h1>Good Everywhere™</h1></span></div><div data-rid="c7629863-4086-4d52-a424-924725629ddd" class="r-19rz72x"><div data-rid="a30a8d1d-bf11-4cca-b829-af32f5d19ce2" class="r-1asloz7"><div data-rid="4584586f-06de-4132-a926-b0ebb0d9ceab" class="r-cnlbqg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>10%</p></span></div><div data-rid="ea2100f3-d1f1-42ab-8654-3704c09f5962" class="r-19yuu1n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Profits Given Away</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="0e4aa6e8-af77-40ca-8230-08ffcc00eeba" class="r-1sreuv"><div data-rid="76afe420-6248-4efc-a279-9785cf0670c5" class="r-iqsmhk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>$10M</p></span></div><div data-rid="e83e4433-381a-4bef-ba61-0bd18aea84a2" class="r-1n2mkqw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>In Total Donations</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="9b67bd8a-d117-4bea-942e-eeb8e1f6374f" class="r-ta3yom"><div data-rid="240d0e3a-510f-4bf1-80fa-f70731f19736" class="r-1u42y2k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>1000+</p></span></div><div data-rid="175048ee-c760-499b-92c3-8b5b7f1bfa31" class="r-asqhvh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Nonprofits Reached</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="a38276fb-6b7f-4838-8dba-5466f5a570ea" class="r-16nhpic alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>We exist to give generously. Since starting in 2016, we have given away over $10M to more than 1,000 non-profits. As a leading drinkware and consumer goods company, Simple Modern gives at least 10% of annual profits to communities around the world, equaling millions in donations since the company’s founding in 2015.</p></span></div><div data-rid="64666ac0-bb81-4954-8363-c9e59630ab57" class="r-12ukfh5"><div style="aspect-ratio:var(--rar, auto);width:100%;height:var(--rhe)"></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="f7c370d7-e048-473c-bea7-d4a7bee7019b" class="r-1ws4kev"><div data-rid="92be09ae-59e0-4603-a31e-8b354a43f3da" class="r-1i7hjd2"><div data-rid="eba832a1-a7c1-4358-a15d-8525